\section{Details}{
  With this control class, contamination is modeled as a two-step process.  The 
  first step is to randomly select observations to be contaminated, the second 
  is to model the distribution of the outliers.  In this case, the values of 
  the contaminated observations will be generated by the function given by slot 
  \code{distribtion} and will not depend on on the original values.
}
